{"tid":1243530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣組］ 香港人只會團結，政府建制先會割席！","createTime":"2019-06-19T13:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T00:25:51.000Z","uid":229880,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7b723958d46bb7a1a4831b0649093430ed9a4a","tid":1243530,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"621前嘅準備<br />\n<br />\n有見政府連日割席話前線責任，自損50士氣後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我地講明唔會割席，香港人絕對同建制中人唔同！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因此，我地有以下嘅文宣方向，目標係團結大家，以下係幾個初步建議：<br />\n<br />\n1. 致敬所有612、連日前線嘅人。特別係受咗創傷嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 感激受牽連嘅無怨無悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 倡議檢討警權問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 自發啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎自由製圖、文宣<br />\n<br />\n我地必須團結！絕不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b48837a82b10f025c3dae3a0ea88399a12a724","tid":1243530,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推"},{"pid":"9de267255cd938591ef62f6a2a2d1386994405a2","tid":1243530,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"bd9d429a3ad14cd1ac47f7fb2f8fe67256bdd4b2","tid":1243530,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:28:41.000Z","msg":"推多一下"},{"pid":"72c367faf948c0f5773850d031f5f9a0b9eab6cc","tid":1243530,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:28:54.000Z","